                            <div class="open-sans-nama">Ahmad Farhad</div>
                            <div class="open-sans-role">Founder of Gymgym</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!--4-->
                <div class="col ">
                    <div class="row isi">
                        <img class="foto"
                            src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQHEIn3WIBXiQg/profile-displayphoto-scale_200_200/B56ZfqZzIJHEAc-/0/1751984326507?e=1775088000&v=beta&t=HaGdRoV9C5-EMkq8E9Wk0qb8O4YvSnbtj8An1mcYIWE">
                        <div class="col keterangan">
                            <P class="open-sans-kalimat">"Kerja sama yang sangat menyenangkan. Tim sangat ramah dan
